body_text:
That is expected to fail. We manuqlly mirror dependencies on GCS once the
links are updated.

On Jul 18, 2017 8:16 AM, "Nayana Thorat" <notifications@github.com> wrote:

@gunan <https://github.com/gunan> Thanks for your reply.
I was a preparing patch for tensorflow/workspace.bzl file for PR however
getting an issue with below link:
//mirror.bazel.build/github.com/google/farmhash/archive/
23eecfbe7e84ebf2e229bd02248f431c36e12f1a.zip"

on wget, it gives an error as:
HTTP request sent, awaiting response... 403 Forbidden

Am I missing something here?

Also the patch requires sha256 for farmhash commit id. I have calculated
sha256 for farmhash commit id 23eecfbe7e84ebf2e229bd02248f431c36e12f1a as
55215f8cd3ddbe9781f6fe5cc228731d6dcc8301b6191c6d420034c3fff1cb8d.
can you please confirm if it's correct?
